ness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32653,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/05\/knowledge-reward-acted-on-it\/","url_meta":{"origin":1064,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Knowledge: They have reward of those who act on it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Anas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever imparts knowledge will have the reward of whoever acted upon it, without detracting from the reward of one who acted.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 240 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0630\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32651,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/05\/three-best-things-leave-behind\/","url_meta":{"origin":1064,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Three best things to leave behind after death","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Qatadah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best of what a man leaves behind are three: a righteous child who supplicates for him, ongoing charity the reward of which reaches him, and knowledge that is acted upon after him.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":1758,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/12\/22\/plant-tree-reward-charity\/","url_meta":{"origin":1064,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Every tree a Muslim plants is rewarded as charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 22, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas bin Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo Muslim plants a tree or sows a seed and then a bird, or a human, or an animal eats from it but that it is charity for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2320, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":43669,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/05\/08\/four-types-sadaqat-jariyah\/","url_meta":{"origin":1064,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Charity: Four types of Sadaqah Jariyah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 8, 2025","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFour people continue to be rewarded after death: a soldier guarding the frontier in the way of Allah, one teaching a good deed to others is rewarded like them as they act upon it, a man\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousne